name: Warmup_Div01_Sub02
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD1S2.CPF,
GmailD1S2.NOME,
GmailD1S2.EMAIL,
GmailD1S2.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S2.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD1S2.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD1S2.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S2.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV01_SUB02 GmailD1S2
UNION
